rosnode : display node info
rosnode list
rosnode cleanup
roscore : start master node

rosrun : run a node
rosrun rqt_graph rqt_graph : graph all internode comunication streams
rosrun rqt_plot rqt_plot : plot messages on a chart
rosrun rqt_console rqt_console : show node console output
rosrun rqt_logger_level rqt_logger_level : logger

rostopic : list all rostopic commands
rostopic list -h : all rostopic list commands
rostopic pub : allows you to publish a message (rostopic pub [topic] [msg_type] [args])

rosservice : commands that can be used on topics
rosservice list : list commands
rosservice call [commands] : calls command
rosservice type [command] | rossrv show : show all command parameters

rosparam : set and examine data on the ROS parameter server
rosparam list
rosparam set
rosparam get
rosparam dump 
rosparam load

roslaunch [package] [filename.launch] : launches nodes based on a launch file

roscp [package_name] [file_to_copy_path] [copy_path] : copies file from one ros package to another

rosmsg : create a ros message
rosmsg show <message type>
rossrv show <service type>

roswtf : debug tool. Shows all errors.

rospack plugins --attrib=plugin controller_interface     see all controller plugins

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MAKE INSTRUCTIONS:
$ cd ~/catkin_ws
$ catkin_make
$ . ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash

note: added source ./devel/setup.bash to ~/.bashrc. Runs setup.bash on terminal startup
